Interface CommonDeploymentMechanism

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DeploymentMechanism
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DebianDeploymentMechanism, RedhatDeploymentMechanism
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CommonDeploymentMechanismImpl, DebianDeploymentMechanismImpl, RedhatDeploymentMechanismImpl

    public interface CommonDeploymentMechanism
extends DeploymentMechanism
    A representation of the model object 'Common Deployment Mechanism'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Changes
    • Maintainer
